Title: Relates to establishing a commission to rename the Robert Moses State Park to reflect on the history of Long Island
Summary: Establishes a nine member commission to rename the Robert Moses State Park to reflect on the history of Long Island.
ActClause: AN ACT to establish a temporary state commission to rename the Robert Moses State Park; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
